 <Para 
  <Unique 78682922>
  <PgfTag `s10i'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77354251>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `The assessee had sold receivables and payables of inter-corporate deposits '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `from its parent E group of companies to its sister concern, IA, resulting in '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `loss which it claimed as a deduction. The Assessing Officer held the transac'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `tion to be sham and the loss fictitious, not allowable as a bad debt or business '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `loss.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78682926>
  <PgfTag `s10i'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77354295>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `The assessee had incurred interest expenses and also earned interest '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `income. No interest had been charged on certain deposits for reasons of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `commercial expediency. The Commissioner (Appeals) categorically noted '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `that on the question whether the funds borrowed were used for business '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `purposes, no details were furnished by the assessee.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78682930>
  <PgfTag `s10i'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77354339>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `The assessee had made investment in company EL, which it claimed was '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `meant for EL to carry out trading activity. However, no such activity could '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `be carried out because of prevalent market conditions. These shares were '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `brought back from the assessee resulting in a loss to the assessee. Over and '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `above the loss, the assessee had also debited finance cost in its books of account '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `incurred towards this investment. Before the Assessing Officer, no document '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `in relation thereto was produced and the record showed that no business '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `happened in EL. Therefore, the Assessing Officer held that as nothing was '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `brought on record to prove that the investment was in relation to the '>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FDW  -0.6%>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String `asses'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `see’s business, he disallowed the interest expenditure, which the Commissioner'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String ` '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `(Appeals) confirmed.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
