   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 78683389>
    <ETag `Bold'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `3.'>
   <ElementEnd `Bold'>
   <String ` '>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String `Fact shows that the assessee is a company engaged in the business of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `handling crude oil and petroleum products. Its facility consists of an off'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `shore single-point mooring, two jetties for handling liquid petroleum '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `products, tanks for storage of crude oil and petroleum products and rail '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `and road gantries for dispatch of petroleum products.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683398>
  <PgfTag `s10'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77300545>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Font 
    <FTag `Bold'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77358606>
    <ETag `Bold'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `4.'>
   <ElementEnd `Bold'>
   <String ` '>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String `The '>
   <String `a'>
   <String `ssessee filed its return of income on February 8, 2018 declaring a '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `total loss of Rs. 203,979,700 and computed the book profit under section '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `115JB at a loss of Rs. 8,822,243,600. The return of income was picked up for '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `scrutiny by issue of notice under section 143(2) of the act on August 27, '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `2018 and further notice under section 142(1) of the '>
   <String `A'>
   <String `ct was also issued.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683405>
  <PgfTag `s10'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77301074>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Font 
    <FTag `Bold'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77358682>
    <ETag `Bold'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `5.'>
   <ElementEnd `Bold'>
   <String ` '>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String `After scrutiny, the assessment order was passed under section 143(3) '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `of the '>
   <String `A'>
   <String `ct on December 28, 2019, wherein the total income of the assessee '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `was assessed at Rs. 5,605,920,300 and the book profit remained '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `unchanged.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683412>
  <PgfTag `s10'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77301600>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Font 
    <FTag `Bold'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77358705>
    <ETag `Bold'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `6.'>
   <ElementEnd `Bold'>
   <String ` '>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String `Against this, '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `assessee preferred an appeal before the learned '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Commissioner of Income-tax (Appeals), wherein appellate order was '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `passed on February 25, 2022 dismissing the appeal of the assessee. There'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `fore, '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `assessee is in appeal before us. Before us '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `assessee has filed a '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `rectified form 36'>
   <String ` '>
   <String `which is taken on record.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683422>
  <PgfTag `s10'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77302123>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Font 
    <FTag `Bold'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77358726>
    <ETag `Bold'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `7.'>
   <ElementEnd `Bold'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String ` '>
   <String `The '>
   <String `a'>
   <String `ssessee has also made an application for admission of additional '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `evidence and filed a paper book starting from page Nos. 629-914 (paper '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `book-III) as additional evidence containing eighteen documents. Out of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `that it was stated that thirteen documents are already part of '>
   <String `D'>
   <String `epartmental '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `records however not submitted during the assessment proceedings for '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `assessment year 2017-18. With respect to documents mentioned at serial '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FDW  -1.0%>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String `No. 14 is a memorandum of association of the company, board note relating'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String ` '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `to investments in Enneagon Ltd. Mauritius (serial No. 15), audited financial '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `statements of Enneagon Ltd. Mauritius (serial No. 16) and board resolution '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `for assignment of receivables and payable (serial No. 17) are the additional '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `evidence. At serial No. 18 '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `assessee has submitted the computation of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `income for the assessment year 2017-18. With respect to serial Nos. 1 to 13 '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <TextRectID 70>
   <String `the contention of the assessee was that about documents are part '>
   <String `D'>
   <String `epart'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `mental records for the respective assessment years and the Assessing '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Officer has relied on the same in the assessment order for the assessment '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `year 2017-18. The same are now being relied upon by the assessee'>
   <String `-'>
   <String `com'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `pany to substantiate that interest income on inter'>
   <String `-'>
   <String `corporate deposits given '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `by the appellant were offered to tax in respective years in return of income '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `as business income and have been assessed also as business income. '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `Further for documents at serial No. 14 the assessee submitted that one of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the objects of the assessee under the head objects incidental or ancillary to '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the attainment of the more main objects in its memorandum of association '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `which allows the assessee to lend money. The said fact was mentioned by '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the assessee in its submission however neither the Assessing Officer nor '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the Commissioner of Income-tax (Appeals) has called for the copy of this '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `document and therefore '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `assessee wants to rely on the same to '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `substantiate its submission. With respect to documents at serial Nos. 15 '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `and 16 it referred to the board note relating to investment in Ennagoan '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Ltd.'>
   <String `,'>
   <String ` Mauritius discusses and details on the proposal relating to availing of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `financing facility of US$ 450 million and use of proceeds for equity infusion '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `into overseas subsidiary and audited financials of the said subsidiary for the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `year'>
   <String `-'>
   <String `ended March 31, 2017. Both these documents are relied upon by the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `assessee to demonstrate the business rational and the business activity '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `carried out by that subsidiary for the year'>
   <String `-'>
   <String `ended March 31, 2017. With '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `respect to document at serial No. 17 which is a board resolution relating to '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `assignment is to demonstrate that the competent authority of the appellant '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `has taken the decision regarding the said transaction after taking into '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `account the larger scheme of things. It was the claim of the assessee that '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the above documents are relevant documents which could not have been '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `furnished before the lower authorities and therefore those documents must '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `be admitted deciding the issue.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
