  <ParaLine 
   <String `exceptional loss of Rs. 177.54 crores (net of expected credit loss (ECL) '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `of Rs. 73.80 crores) for the year which has been accounted in the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
