   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `proposed to be claimed should be taken into account in computing '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the income of the assessee of the previous year in which this amount '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `of such debt or part thereof is written off or of an earlier year, or'>
