  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683648>
  <PgfTag `Quotation2'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77316744>
    <ETag `Para3'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `3. No business rational has been submitted by the assessee for '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `taking ICDs from a company and advancing it to the shareholders/'>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `subsidiaries of that same company, suggesting that these transactions '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `are not out of usual business transaction.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para3'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683652>
  <PgfTag `Quotation2'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77317167>
    <ETag `Para3'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `4. Inter'>
   <String `-'>
   <String `corporate deposits are instruments in which, the initia'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `tion is at the instance of the depositor, i. e., the giver who has surplus '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `funds, as against in the case of a loan where the transaction is '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `initiated at the instance of the borrower who is in need of the money. '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Further in the case of an ICD, the amount is repayable on demand '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `whereas a loan is repayable on the conclusion of the agreed tenure. '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `The assessee has booked interest cost to forward ICDs to group '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `concern. This is against the very nature of an ICD. The ICD should be '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `out of surplus funds with the company.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para3'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683656>
  <PgfTag `Quotation2'>
  <ParaLine 
   <TextRectID 80>
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77317587>
    <ETag `Para3'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `5. That during the previous assessment proceedings the assessee '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `has failed to prove that borrowed money had not been utilised for '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `non-business purposes. This is fact on record reference is drawn to '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `previous assessment orders of the assessee.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para3'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683663>
  <PgfTag `Quotation2'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77318004>
    <ETag `Para3'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `6. That additions were made by the Assessing Officer on account '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `of interest claimed under section 36(1)(iii) of the Act.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para3'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683667>
  <PgfTag `Quotation1'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77318418>
    <ETag `Para2'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `4.5.4 Without prejudice to the facts mentioned above, this is not a '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `case where the debts were written off due to inability in recovering '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the debts, but write off has happened as a result of assignment of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `such debts to the assessee’s group company Ibrox Aviation '>
   <String `a'>
   <String `nd '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `Trading P. Ltd. (IATPL) in a single accounting year the assessee has '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `assigned the dates to a group company (which is not an asset recon'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `struction company) and has taken a haircut of whooping Rs. 251.30 '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `crores in its books of account. The transaction with IATPL is '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `discussed in paragraph 3.7 in detail. Further as discussed in the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `preceding paragraph in the case of an ICD, the amount is repayable '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `on demand whereas the loan is repayable on the conclusion of the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `agreed tenure. Had the assessee had doubts about a particular ICD '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `being recovered back, it would have recalled the ICD in that year '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `itself.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para2'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683672>
  <PgfTag `Quotation1'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 78683671>
    <ETag `Para2'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `4.5.5 '>
   <String `I'>
   <String `t is thus clear from the facts mentioned above that the asses'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `see in previous year had advanced ICDs to its group concerns from '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the ICDs from group entities and loans taken from financial institu'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `tions. That such advances made to group concerns have been written '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `off during the year not on account of failure to recover the debts, but '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `on account of reassignment of such deposits to a group concern. '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Against the reassignment of net deposits worth Rs. 250 crores, the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `assessee has received a sum of Rs. 4.8 crores. As a result, the assessee '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `has booked a loss of Rs. 251.30 crores. It is thus clear that this is not a '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `case of advance turning bad, but a sham transaction to book '>
   <String `fictitious'>
   <String ` '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `expenses in the books of account.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para2'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683676>
  <PgfTag `Quotation1'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77319237>
    <ETag `Para2'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `4.6 Again, vide submissions dated December 24, 2019 the assessee '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `stated that the loss incurred on ICDs and security along with accrued '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `interest is allowable as deduction under section 36(1)(vii) read with '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `section 36(2) and under section 28(i). The submissions of the assessee '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `are not acceptable. The conditions in relation to business loss are '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `clear :'>
   <ElementEnd `Para2'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683681>
  <PgfTag `Quotation2'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77319642>
    <ETag `Para3'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `1. That it should be incidental to the carrying on of the business.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para3'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683685>
  <PgfTag `Quotation2'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77320044>
    <ETag `Para3'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `2. Should be on revenue account.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para3'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683689>
  <PgfTag `Quotation2'>
  <ParaLine 
   <TextRectID 82>
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77320443>
    <ETag `Para3'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `3. Should be a real loss and not a notional fictitious one.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para3'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683692>
  <PgfTag `Quotation2'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77320839>
    <ETag `Para3'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `4. Should have actually been incurred and not anticipated as '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `certain to occur in future.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para3'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683696>
  <PgfTag `Quotation2'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77321232>
    <ETag `Para3'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `5. Should not be prohibited from being deducted under the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `provisions of the '>
   <String `A'>
   <String `ct.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para3'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683700>
  <PgfTag `Quotation1'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77321622>
    <ETag `Para2'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `Hence the loss was not incidental to the business, nor was of a '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `revenue account. It was a future anticipated loss. Clearly the loss '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `claimed on ICD is not allowable under section 28(i) of the '>
   <String `A'>
   <String `ct.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para2'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683704>
  <PgfTag `Quotation1'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77322009>
    <ETag `Para2'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `4.7 Agreement with Ibrox Aviation '>
   <String `a'>
   <String `nd Trading P. Ltd. : As '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `discussed above the assessee has booked loss on account of assign'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `ment of debts to its group concern IATPL. IATPL is an Essar '>
   <String `g'>
   <String `roup '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `company and is not an asset reconstruction company. In fact, IATPL '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `is a shareholder of Essar '>
   <String `O'>
   <String `il. Essar '>
   <String `O'>
   <String `il has advanced ICDs to VPTL '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `and VOTL'>
   <String ` '>
   <String `the agreement to assign certain assets and liabilities of the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `assessee'>
   <String `-'>
   <String `company to IATPL was executed on March 31, 2017. In the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `agreement Essar '>
   <String `P'>
   <String `orts and '>
   <String `S'>
   <String `hipping Ltd., Mauritius has acted as the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `guarantor.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para2'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683708>
  <PgfTag `Quotation1'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77322393>
    <ETag `Para2'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `4.7.2 As per the agreement with VOTL the seller of identified '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `assets and liabilities would sell its assets and liabilities to IATPL for a '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `consideration of Rs. 4.8 crores. The identified assets total to Rs. 955.4 '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `crores. The assets where ICDs advanced by the assessee to five '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `entities that are either subsidiaries or shareholders of Essar '>
   <String `O'>
   <String `il. The '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `identified liabilities were Rs. 699 crores of ICD the assessee owed to '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Essar '>
   <String `O'>
   <String `il Ltd. Thus, net assets of Rs. 256.4 crores were assigned to '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `IATPL. Against such assignment IATPL paid a sum of Rs. 4.8 crores '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `to the assessee. The differential amount of Rs. 251.3 crores were '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `booked by the assessee as loss in its books of account.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para2'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683712>
  <PgfTag `Quotation1'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77322774>
    <ETag `Para2'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `4.7.3 Clearly the entire transaction is an intragroup arrangement, '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `which has led to '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `assessee claiming a loss of Rs. 251.6 crores. The '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `loss is a national one and not actual loss. The assessee has brought '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `nothing on record to show that efforts were made to recover the ICD '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `before assigning the same to a group concern at a steep haircut.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para2'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683716>
  <PgfTag `Quotation1'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77323152>
    <ETag `Para2'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `4.8 In the light of the facts brought out in the preceding para'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `graphs, the loss claimed by the assessee of Rs. 251.30 crores on '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `account of company’s inability to collect ICD and interest thereon, the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `amount specified is disallowed. Penalty proceedings under section '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `270A of the Income-tax Act are initiated separately for misreporting '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `and under'>
   <String `-'>
   <String `reporting of income.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para2'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
