 <Para 
  <Unique 78683740>
  <PgfTag `s10'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77324268>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Font 
    <FTag `Bold'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77359915>
    <ETag `Bold'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `17.'>
   <ElementEnd `Bold'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String ` '>
   <String `The '>
   <String `a'>
   <String `ssessee challenged this addition before the learned Commis'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `sioner of Income-tax (Appeals). In para Nos. 5.1 to 5.7 the learned '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `Commissioner of Income-tax has discussed the proceedings before the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `learned Assessing Officer. In paragraph No. 5.8 onwards the findings of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the learned Commissioner of Income-tax (Appeals) are rendered as under :'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683753>
  <PgfTag `Quotation1'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77347032>
    <ETag `Quote'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77324634>
    <ETag `Para2'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `”5.8 At the appellate stage, the appellant has contended that loss '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `arising on transfer of ICDs is allowable as a deduction. However, if '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the assessee had doubts about a particular ICD being recovered back '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `it would have recalled the ICD in that year itself instead of bearing '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `loss arising on transfer. Here the loss was not incidental to the busi'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `ness, nor was of revenue account. As pointed out by the Assessing '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Officer, the assessee has booked a loss on account of assignment of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `debts to its group concern IATPL. IATPL is Essar group company and '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `is not an asset reconstruction company. In the fact, IATPL is a share'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `holder of Essar Oil. Essar '>
   <String `O'>
   <String `il had advanced ICDs to VPTL and VOTL '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `and the agreement to assign certain assets and liability of the asses'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `see'>
   <String `-'>
   <String `company to IATPL was executed on March 31, 2017. Appellant’s '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `contention that the loss on account of company’s inability to collect '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the amount specified of Rs. 251.30 crores cannot be entertained since, '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `it has not proven or made any efforts to collect the said amount. The '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `appellant has failed to prove that how it was unable to collect the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `amount also brought nothing on record to show that efforts were '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `made to recover the ICD before assigning the same to a group '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `concern.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para2'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683760>
  <PgfTag `Quotation1'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77325010>
    <ETag `Para2'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `5.9 '>
   <String `I'>
   <String `n this respect, the appellant has relied upon some case law. '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `However, they are not relevant in the case of appellant. In the case of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
