 <Para 
  <Unique 78683883>
  <PgfTag `Quotation1'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77347231>
    <ETag `Quote'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77328116>
    <ETag `Para2'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `”'>
   <String `The '>
   <String `a'>
   <String `ssessee has filed appeal mainly on the issue of disallowance '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `of Rs. 251.30 crores and other additions. For this loss assessee has '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `sold its and certain advances of Rs. 955 crores and liabilities of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Rs.'>
   <Char EnSpace>
   <String `6,99 crores to a related party for a consideration of only Rs. 4.8 '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `crore'>
   <String `s'>
   <String ` and claimed deduction of Rs. 251 crores. The assessment order '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `clearly states that there is no business rational of above transaction. '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `On reading of annual report also we found that there is a scheme of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `arrangement and change in holding company, in the auditor’s report '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `there is a qualification and management reply thereto. As per note '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `No. 56 of annual report, it is evident that the above transactions are '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `offshoot of larger understanding between Essar '>
   <String `O'>
   <String `il Ltd. entering into '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `share purchase agreement. Therefore, rational of sale of assets worth '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Rs. 955 crores included in the above when it is realising interest, sold '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `by the assessee along with liability of Rs. 6'>
   <String `.'>
   <String `99 crores for Rs. 4.8 crores '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `only need to be examined. The authorised representative is directed '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `to explain the same.”'>
   <ElementEnd `Para2'>
   <ElementEnd `Quote'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683891>
  <PgfTag `s10'>
  <ParaLine 
   <TextRectID 93>
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77328433>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Font 
    <FTag `Bold'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77360663>
    <ETag `Bold'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `24.'>
   <ElementEnd `Bold'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String ` In response to the above order sheet enquiry from the '>
   <String `B'>
   <String `ench, the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `assessee submitted a letter dated May 20, 2024. '>
   <String `The '>
   <String `l'>
   <String `earned authorised '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FDW  -1.0%>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String `representative invited our attention to press note placed at page No. 948-947'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String ` '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `of '>
   <Font 
    <FTag `Italics'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77360783>
    <ETag `Italics'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `Business Today'>
   <ElementEnd `Italics'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String ` wherein it was stated that Essar Rosneft'>
   <String ` '>
   <String `C'>
   <String `omplete deal '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `worth US'>
   <String ` '>
   <String `$ 12.9 billion. He further submitted that various news reports '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `placed at page Nos. 915 to 1026 are publicly available documents which '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `explains the rationale of the above deal. He further submitted that on '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `attention to page No. 231 is again that '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `assessee has transferred both '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the assets and liabilities. The inter'>
   <String `-'>
   <String `corporate deposits were an asset having '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the grave doubt about recovery of the amount. '>
   <String `The '>
   <String `assessee was hopeful if '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `there is a change in shareholding there would be improvement in the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `chances of recovery. He referred to 5 inter'>
   <String `-'>
   <String `corporate deposits which were '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `doubtful of recovery part of the transfer he also referred to liability payable '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `of Rs. 699 crores also part of the transferred asset. With reference to the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `rational, he referred to paper book page Nos. 1027 to 1044 which is a credit '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `rating for bank facilities of Vadinar Oil Terminal Ltd. by care ratings dated '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `May 23, 2018. He referred to page No. 1030 wherein detailed rational of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Essar '>
   <String `O'>
   <String `il Ltd. was mentioned in that report. He referred to page No. 1035 '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `of that care ratings report relating to Vadinar Oil '>
   <String `T'>
   <String `erminal Ltd. He further '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `referred to the financial statement of the assessee for the assessment year'>
   <String `s'>
   <String ` '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `2018-19 to 2020-21 to show that there is a decline in interest cost, there is '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `decrease in borrowing there is increase in gross revenue and corresponding '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `increase in profit before taxes. Thus, he submitted that change in share'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `holders and transfer of assets and liabilities is for the benefit of assessee-'>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `company and that is the justification why the assets and liabilities are '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `transferred together. It was further stated that the interest is not realised '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `but accrued to the assessee and is outstanding. It was further submitted '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `that transfer of these assets is based on the valuation report of grant '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Thornton issued in April 2017 and therefore the transaction made by the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `assessee is for the benefit of the assessee.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683901>
  <PgfTag `s10'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
