    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77360905>
    <ETag `Bold'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `27.'>
   <ElementEnd `Bold'>
   <String ` '>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String `The learned authorised representative further referred to the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `response of the management on the qualification in the audit report '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `wherein it is mentioned that after due consideration, the company sold the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `portfolio of outstanding receivables amounting to Rs. 2'>
   <String `,'>
   <String `569.42 crore'>
   <String `s'>
   <String ` and '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `payable is amounting to Rs. 2'>
   <String `,'>
   <String `298.21 crore'>
   <String `s'>
   <String ` from certain related and other '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `entities to Essar '>
   <String `S'>
   <String `teel Jharkhand Ltd. and Ibrox Aviation and Trading '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `P.'>
   <Char EnSpace>
   <String `Ltd., at fair valuation. On the basis of fair valuation of these outstanding '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `receivables and payables, the company has debited to the profit and loss '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Rs. 177.50 crores as an exceptional item, the company expects to realise the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `carrying values of the investment and other deals through the escrow '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `arrangement shortly. Therefore, there was a justification and rational for '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the above deal.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683925>
  <PgfTag `s10'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77329671>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Font 
    <FTag `Bold'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77360932>
    <ETag `Bold'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `28.'>
   <ElementEnd `Bold'>
   <String ` '>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String `The learned Commissioner of Income-tax-Departmental represent'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `ative vehemently supported the order of the learned lower authorities and '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `stated that it is a sham transaction as stated by the learned Assessing '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Officer confirmed by the learned Commissioner of Income-tax (Appeals)'>
   <String `.'>
   <String ` '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `The assessee has not submitted the relevant document before the lower '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `authorities on this issue. Further the clubbing of the assets and liabilities '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `together does not have any rational. He further stated that the deduction is '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `neither available as bad debt as claimed by the assessee before the learned '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Assessing Officer and not also as a business loss. He further submitted that '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the learned Assessing Officer has given a detail reason which are not '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `controverted by the assessee.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683938>
  <PgfTag `s10'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77329973>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Font 
    <FTag `Bold'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77360941>
    <ETag `Bold'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `29.'>
   <ElementEnd `Bold'>
   <String ` '>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String `The learned Commissioner of Income-tax-Departmental represent'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `ative further submitted that all the decision cited by the learned authorised '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `representative are taking the claim that the claim of the assessee is under '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the head bad debt, it is not about that but a sham transaction which has '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `been claimed as a deduction or business loss by the assessee. He submitted '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `that when the gross assets of the value of Rs. 955 crores which are earning '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `good income along with the liability of Essar '>
   <String `O'>
   <String `il Ltd. of Rs. 699.29 crores '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `having the net asset value of Rs. 256.09 crores are sold to a sister concern '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `for only Rs. 4.79 crores itself shows that the transaction is sham.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683945>
  <PgfTag `s10'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77330272>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Font 
    <FTag `Bold'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77360964>
    <ETag `Bold'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `30.'>
   <ElementEnd `Bold'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String ` He further submitted that there is a qualification in the auditor’s '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `report wherein there is a qualified opinion is given by the auditor. He '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `further referred to the profit and loss account of the assessee wherein as '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `per note No. 40 a sum of Rs. 918.68 crores have been written off. He '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `further referred to note No. 40 wherein a sum of Rs. 177.50 crores have '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `been debited to the profit and loss account as specified in note No. 56. He '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <TextRectID 97>
   <String `also took us to note No. 56, wherein there is an offshoot of the transaction '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `of sale of major shareholders of the Essar '>
   <String `O'>
   <String `il Ltd. selling the stake to the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `third parties and thereafter several agreements entered wherein this sum is '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `mentioned. The assessee has failed to produce despite the '>
   <String `B'>
   <String `ench asking for '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the same agreement. He further stated that if the assessee is not aware or '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `not in possession of that agreement how it can refer to in the annual '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `accounts of the assessee and then make a reference of the provision of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `investment. He further referred to note No. 16 and not'>
   <String `e'>
   <String ` No. 21 which are '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `also interlinked. Therefore, his argument was that '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `assessee is hiding '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `behind the original agreement entered by the majority shareholders of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Essar '>
   <String `O'>
   <String `il Ltd. with third'>
   <String `-'>
   <String `party. He therefore submitted that the claim of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the assessee is neither bona fide, nor allowable under the provisions of the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `law and is based on hidden facts.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683952>
  <PgfTag `s10'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77330568>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Font 
    <FTag `Bold'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77361048>
    <ETag `Bold'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `31.'>
   <ElementEnd `Bold'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String ` We have carefully considered the rival contention and perused the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `orders of the learned lower authorities. Short issue involved in this appeal '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `is that when '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `assessee has transferred its certain financial assets along '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `with certain financial liabilities for a consideration to a sister concern, loss '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `arising thereon whether should be considered as bad debt, deductible as a '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `business loss or it is not at all allowable to the assessee.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78683959>
  <PgfTag `s10'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77330861>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Font 
    <FTag `Bold'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77361060>
    <ETag `Bold'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `32.'>
   <ElementEnd `Bold'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String ` The facts succinctly stated shows that '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `assessee has transferred '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `certain inter corporate deposits with its group companies (Essar '>
