    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `“The company had receivable from various group companies and '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `other entities, operating in steel, shipping, and other sectors. Due to '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the weakening of the sectors and data duration of the financial '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `condition (including restructuring of that is) of these entities, a situ'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `ation has arise in wherein the value of the receivables from these '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `entities has significantly declined and recovery of their dues is likely '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `to take a substantial amount of time. The company, therefore, we, '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `after considering the report of an independent third-party, its ability '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `to collect the outstanding balances.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para2'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78684245>
  <PgfTag `Quotation1'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77341686>
    <ETag `Para2'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `Further, as reported in the earlier year, controlling stake being '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `non-public shareholding in the company was to be acquired by Essar '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `O'>
   <String `il Ltd. (EOL) as a condition precedent to the share purchase agree'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `ments (SPA) executed on October 15, 2016 by the majority stake'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `holders of EOL to sell their shareholding to Petrol Complex Pte Ltd. '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `and Kesani Enterprises Co'>
   <String `.'>
   <String ` Ltd. As a result, the company will no '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `longer remain a part of the Essar group and accordingly the company '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `intends to settle all its assets and liabilities and realise the dues from '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `related parties and other entities as envisaged in the transaction '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `documents exist to pursuant to the SPAs.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para2'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
