   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String ` We find that '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `assessee has produced the report of Grant Thorton '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `in April 2017 on recoverable values of receivables from Essar '>
