   <String ` '>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String `We find that in the resolution there is no reference of any loss '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `incurred on transfer of the asset, valuation of inter corporate deposits at fair '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `market value, to who these assets are to be sold, which assets are to be sold '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `to which entity, and whether the draft agreement has been perused by the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `board before entering into. Further it is apparent that the agreement of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `transfer of receivable entered by the assessee with Ibrox '>
   <String `A'>
   <String `viation and '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `T'>
   <String `erminals P. Ltd., produced before us is an unsigned document. Therefore, '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the production of this board resolution which has not discussed any '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `rational of selling of inter corporate deposits given at substantial discount, '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `does not help the case of the assessee.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
