  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `O'>
   <String `il Ltd. (EOL) as a condition precedent to the share purchase '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `agreements (SPA) executed on October 15, 2016 by the majority '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `stakeholders of EOL to sell their shareholding to '>
   <String `P'>
   <String `etrol '>
   <String `C'>
   <String `omplex Pte '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Ltd. and Kesani Enterprises Co'>
   <String `.'>
   <String ` Ltd. As a result, the company will no '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `longer remain a part of the Essar group and accordingly the company '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `intends to settle all its assets and liabilities and realise the dues from '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `related parties and other entities as envisaged in the transaction '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `documents exist to pursuant to the SPAs.”'>
