   <String `that agreement, how the assessee is not having any access to that docu'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `ment. The non-production of such document goes against the assessee '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `because for proving the genuineness of the transaction, onus lies on the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `assessee. Merely relying on the press notes and newspapers items without '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <TextRectID 111>
   <String `looking at the agreement to which '>
