   <String ` '>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String `Therefore, we do not find any infirmity in the order of the learned '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Assessing Officer in denying the deduction of the loss of Rs. 177.5 crores '>
  > # end of ParaLine
