   <String ` '>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String `The learned authorised representative specifically referred that it is '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `not the case of the learned Assessing Officer that '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `assessee should have '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `earned interest on IC'>
   <String `D'>
   <String `s of Essar '>
   <String `O'>
   <String `il Ltd. and Essar Dredging Ltd. In earlier '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `years, those inter corporate deposits were carrying on interest. He referred '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `to the decision of the honourable Supreme Court '>
