   <String ` '>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String `In this regard, the learned authorised representative further submitted '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `that basis certain information that the assessee has purchased certain '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `immovable property and has made cash payment of Rs. 40,00,000, a show '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `cause was issued under section 148A(b) of the Act by '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `Income-tax '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Officer'>
   <String `,'>
   <String ` Ward-1, Nabha on March 2, 2023 as to why notice under section '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `148 should not be issued on the basis of information that income charge'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `able to tax has escaped assessment. In response, the assessee filed her sub'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `mission and thereafter, '>
   <String `an '>
   <String `order under section 148A(d) was passed on '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `March 30, 2023 and on the same date, i. e., March 30, 2022, notice under '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `section 148 was issued by Income-tax Officer, Ward, Nabha being the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `jurisdictional Assessing Officer.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78695091>
  <PgfTag `s10'>
  <ParaLine 
