    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `“6. We have duly considered the rival contentions and gone '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `through the record carefully. Admittedly, notice under section 148 '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `was issued after the '>
   <String `n'>
   <String `otification issued by the Ministry of Finance, '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Government of India on March 29, 2022. The notice under section '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `148 has been issued on March 29, 2023, i. e., almost one year from the '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `n'>
   <String `otification. Thus, facts of other year are squarely applicable. The '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <TextRectID 138>
   <String `issue in dispute is covered by the judgment of the hon’ble jurisdic'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `tional High Court which read as under :'>
   <ElementEnd `Para2'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78695118>
  <PgfTag `Quotation2'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
