   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `7. Respectfully following the judgment of the hon’ble High Court, '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `we allow the ground of appeal of '>
   <String `c'>
   <String `ross'>
   <String `-'>
   <String `o'>
   <String `bjection and hold that notice '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `issued under section 148 of the Income-tax Act in '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `assessment '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `year 2019-20 is bad in the eyes of law. It was without jurisdiction. '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Accordingly, reassessment order is quashed.'>
