    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `9.'>
   <ElementEnd `Bold'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String ` The learned '>
   <String `s'>
   <String `enior Departmental representative is heard who has '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `fairly submitted that though there are decisions of the hon’ble Punjab and '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Haryana High Court, however, the Revenue is in appeal before the hon’ble '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Supreme Court against such decisions rendered by the hon’ble High Court. '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `However, the learned '>
   <String `s'>
   <String `enior Departmental representative has fairly '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <Char DiscHyphen>
   <String `submitted that there is no stay which has been granted by the hon’ble '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Supreme Court against the decision rendered by the hon’ble Punjab and '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Haryana High Court. Further, he has relied on the order'>
   <String `s'>
   <String ` of the lower '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `authorities.'>
   <ElementEnd `Para'>
  > # end of ParaLine
 > # end of Para
 <Para 
  <Unique 78695280>
  <PgfTag `s10'>
  <ParaLine 
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77266415>
    <ETag `Para'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <Font 
    <FTag `Bold'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77274989>
    <ETag `Bold'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
   <String `10.'>
   <ElementEnd `Bold'>
   <Font 
    <FTag `'>
    <FLocked No>
   > # end of Font
   <String ` I have heard the rival contentions and perused the material available '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `on the record. In the instant case, it is noted that the notice under section '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `148 has been issued on March 30, 2023 by '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `Income-tax Officer'>
   <String `,'>
   <String ` Ward, '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Nabha who is the '>
   <String `j'>
   <String `urisdictional Assessing Officer and not by the Faceless '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Assessment Unit. The said notice has been issued almost after a year from '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the issuance of notification by '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `Ministry of Finance, Government of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `India on March 29, 2022 requiring issuance of notice and conduct of '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `assessment proceedings by the Faceless Assessment Unit. There is thus a '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `clear breach of the binding notification so issued under section 144B '>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `requiring issuance of notices and conduct of proceedings through the Face'>
   <Char SoftHyphen>
  > # end of ParaLine
  <ParaLine 
   <String `less Assessment Unit. The '>
   <String `c'>
   <String `o-ordinate Bench in '>
   <String `the '>
   <String `case of '>
   <ElementBegin 
    <Unique 77267949>
    <ETag `Reference'>
    <Attributes 
    > # end of Attributes
    <Collapsed No>
    <SpecialCase No>
    <AttributeDisplay AllAttributes>
   > # end of ElementBegin
